content:
Use Pre-Chat with an Enhanced Bot

You can use an enhanced bot to gather important customer information and customize a conversation with a bot or agent on Messaging for In-App or Messaging for Web channels.

REQUIRED EDITIONS AND USER PERMISSIONS
Einstein Bots is available in Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience. Setup for Einstein Bots is available in Lightning Experience.
Available in: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

USER PERMISSIONS NEEDED
To build and manage Einstein Bots:
Customize Application
OR
Modify Metadata
OR
Manage Bots

Before you begin, set up pre-chat for Messaging for In-App and Web.

Create Custom Context Variables
Map Your Context Variables
Add Context Variables to Your Bot
